overview: Pako Lorente is a leading brand of high quality designer men’s formal shirts from Poland and the fashion brand is now expanding to the UK with an online presence. As many sophisticated British businessmen know, first impressions are very important. Therefore, it can be very advantageous to be outfitted in the appropriate business attire from the very best designers in order to carry a commanding presence in the meeting room. Many business men are looking to these stylish men’s formal shirts from Poland for their high quality and well-tailored design.
